data.description: Investor's Dream in Palmetto, FL!  Welcome to a prime investment opportunity in Palmetto, just minutes from St. Pete and Tampa to the North, and Brandon/Sarasota to the South.   CURRENT STATUS: This townhome is a unique catch as it is tenant occupied until April 2025. While, now 8 similar townhomes in this community are waiting to be rented, this one is already leased, generating a rental income of $2,500/month and thereby securing your ROI from day one.  FEATURES & LIFESTYLE: With an open layout, GE appliances, and a tranquil lanai, it's perfect for investors eyeing a solid return. Privacy is ensured with a split floor plan, placing bedrooms strategically for comfort. Storage space? Covered with a convenient closet beneath the staircase. Community amenities include a resort-style pool, fire pit, gas grills, and a corn hole area. Edgestone at Artisan Lakes: A maintenance-free community with no CDD fees.   CONVENIENT LOCATION: Near I-75, I-275, US-301, and US-41, it offers easy access to shopping, dining, Ellenton Prime Outlets, and the beach. Palmetto is a rapidly growing waterfront city.   YOUR EXCLUSIVE OPPORTUNITY: 8 identical townhomes are on the market for rental in this beautiful Taylor Morrison, Artisan Lakes Community. But this one is already leased.  Don't pass up this investment opportunity!. Schedule a viewing now and secure your piece of this lucrative investment!
